name: King James.
description: Shot August 9th 2019 on a hot summer weekend in Toronto. This specific weekend Toronto was hosting a mix of celebrities, athletes, and musicians for some of the biggest events. During a private afterparty I was approached by Lebron's Manager and told "He doesn't normal let people take pictures of him, but he has asked if you could shoot a few for him". The view down the lenses of my camera is one that I will never forget, it was almost as if I was face to face with a cardboard cut out, instead it was the legend himself. - Gabriel Di Sante
